Package: foodstorage
Title: Look-up foodco-ops' storage of products
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Poeschl", email = "frumentum@posteo.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains a bunch of functions for calculating the current storage's inventory. Automatically it reports when a new order cycle should be started. For a better visualisation you can find a shiny app inside the package which you can call with the function, runStorageApp().
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), lubridate (>= 1.6.0), shiny (>= 1.0.0), DT (>= 0.2), ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1)
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Import: shinyjs (>= 0.9), shinythemes, colourpicker (>= 0.3), data.table (>= 1.10.4), 
Suggests: testthat
